<td style=" color:#000000; font-size:12pt; background-color:#FFFFFF; font-family:arial; bLabel:main; bEditID:r3st1;" tEditID="c1r1" locked="0" aEditID="c1r1" >
<![CDATA[<div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: right;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; "><font class="Apple-style-span" size="6" color="#000066">{!Contact.SchoolText__c}</font></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: right;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="'Times New Roman', Times, serif" size="4" color="#ff6600"><i>Chartered By The British Schools Foundation</i></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: right;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="6" color="#c0c0c0"><b><i><br></i></b></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: right;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="'Times New Roman', Times, serif" size="1" color="#ff6600"><i><br></i></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><div style="font-family: Times; font-size: medium;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">19th November 2014</font></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="-webkit-border-horizontal-spacing: 5px; -webkit-border-vertical-spacing: 5px; "><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></span></font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="border-spacing: 5px;">Dear&nbsp;{!Contact.Salutation}&nbsp;{!Contact.FirstName}&nbsp;{!Contact.LastName}</span></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div><div style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div><p class="MsoNoSpacing"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">As many of you will be aware, there are sometimes incidents of Hand, Foot and Mouth disease in Malaysia, and unfortunately we have been informed today of 1 case in Year 1. We wanted to alert you to the fact so that you can keep a close eye on your child and keep them at home if any symptoms occur which will help in prevention of spread of disease.</font></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">This morning we conducted the UV light treatment in all classes in KS1 and Sodexo sterilised all utensils.</font></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">The school already has in place the preventative measures listed below.</font></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Prevention and control measures already being used in BSKL:</font></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing"><ol><li><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Good ventilation of classrooms and other places.</span></li><li><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Daily cleaning and disinfection of the door handles, stair railings, bathroom accessories and food utensils using Sodium Hypochlorite 0.5%.</span></li><li><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Early Yearâ€™s toys thoroughly disinfected.</span></li><li><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Unwell children will see nurse and if necessary parents will be contacted.</span></li><li><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">The children have been taught how to wash their hands by teachers.</span></li><li><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Hand washing advice posted in all bathrooms.</span></li></ol></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">The signs and symptoms of hand-foot-and-mouth disease include:</font></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing"><ul><li><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Fever and/or sore throat.</span></li><li><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Painful red blister-like lesions on the tongue, mouth, palms of the hands or soles of the feet.</span></li><li><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Headache and fatigue.</span></li><li><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Irritability in infants and toddlers and loss of appetite.</span></li></ul></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">The usual period from initial infection to the onset of signs and symptoms (incubation period) is three to seven days. Fever is often the first sign of hand-foot-and-mouth disease, followed by a sore throat and sometimes a poor appetite and the feeling of being sick (malaise). One or two days after fever begins, painful sores may develop in the mouth or throat. Rash on the hands and feet can follow within one or two days, and may also appear on the buttocks. Hand-foot-and-mouth disease may cause all of the above signs and symptoms or just a few of them. Please seek immediate medical advice and advise our school nurse promptly if your child is unwell with any of the above symptoms.</font></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Nur Safura</font></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Primary School Nurse</font></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Safura.sabri@britishschool.edu.my</font></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Soo Beng Yee</font></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Secondary School Nurse</font></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">soobeng.yee@britishschool.edu.my</font></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Kind regards</font></p></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Admin Team</font></div></div></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif">{!Contact.SchoolText__c}</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><i><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#ff6600"><b>World Class Education</b></font></i></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif">__________________________________________________________</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="1">{!User.School_List_Email_Footer__c}</font><font class="Apple-style-span" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="1">&nbsp;</font></div>]]></td>
